==Leyenda de Plata 2008== {{Infobox wrestling event |name=''Leyenda de Plata'' (2008) |image=Leyenda De Plata 2008.jpg |caption=Poster for the finals of the 2008 ''Leyenda de Plata'' that also included the 2008 [[CMLL International Gran Prix (2008)|International Gran Prix]] tournament |promotion = [[Consejo Mundial de Lucha Libre]] |date=July 4, 2008 to July 25, 2008 |attendance= |venue=[[Arena Mexico]] |city = [[Mexico City, Mexico]] |liveevent=Y |lastevent=''[[Infierno en el Ring (2008)|Infierno en el Ring]]'' (2008) |nextevent=''[[CMLL Torneo Gran Alternativa#Gran Alternativa 2008|Torneo Gran Alternativa]]'' (2008) |event=''Leyenda de Plata |lastevent2=''[[Leyenda de Plata#Leyenda de Plata 2007|Leyenda de Plata]]'' (2007) |nextevent2=''[[Leyenda de Plata#Leyenda de Plata 2011|Leyenda de Plata]]'' (2011) }} The tenth ''Leyenda de Plata'' took place from July 4 til July 25, 2008. After being forced to withdraw from the 2007 tournament due to an injury [[Perro Aguayo Jr.]] won the first ''cibernetico'' qualifier by outlasting [[Hajime Ohara]], [[Stuka Jr.]], [[El Felino]], [[Ephesto]], [[Averno (wrestler)|Averno]], [[La Mascara (wrestler)|La Máscara]], [[Mephisto (wrestler)|Mephisto]] and [[Volador Jr.]].<ref name=LdP2008-01>{{cite web | url= http://superluchas.net/2008/07/05/resultados-arena-mexico-4-jul-08/ | title= resultados Arena Mexico (4 Jul 08) | author= | date= July 5, 2008 | accessdate= September 23, 2009 | publisher=''SuperLuchas'' Magazine | language=Spanish}}</ref> The following week [[Dr. Wagner Jr.]] also qualified for the semi-final by defeating [[Loco Max]], [[El Sagrado]], [[Máscara Purpura]], [[Virus (wrestler)|Virus]], [[Sangre Azteca]], [[El Hijo del Fantasma]], [[La Sombra (wrestler)|La Sombra]], [[Black Warrior (wrestler)|Black Warrior]] and [[Heavy Metal (wrestler)|Heavy Metal]].<ref name=LdP2008-02>{{cite news|title=Lo Mejor de la Lucha Libre Mexicana 2008|work=SuperLuchas|id=296|date=January 6, 2009|url=http://superluchas.net/?p=11145|accessdate=July 11, 2009|language=Spanish}}</ref> Perro Aguayo Jr. overcame Dr. Wagner Jr. with the help of ''[[Los Perros del Mal]]'' and the 2008 ''Leyenda de Plata'' saw the final that was originally planned for the 2007 tournament as [[Místico]] faced off against Perro Aguayo Jr. As in the semi-final ''Los Perros del Mal'' tried to interfere in the main event but was stopped by Místico's friends [[Héctor Garza]] and [[Dos Caras Jr.]], enabling Místico win ''Leyenda de Plata'' for the third time.<ref name=Leyenda/><ref name=Plata2008/><ref name="LeyendaSL"/><ref name=LdP2008>{{cite web | url= http://superluchas.net/2008/07/25/gran-prix-mexico-resultados-rapidos/ | title= Gran Prix Mexico resultados rapidos | author= | date= July 25, 2008 | accessdate= September 23, 2009 | publisher=''SuperLuchas'' Magazine | language=Spanish}}</ref>
