==Leyenda de Plata 2015== {{Infobox wrestling event |name=''Leyenda de Plata'' (2015) |image=LeyendaDePlata2015.jpg |caption=Official poster for the first part of the ''Leyenda de Plata'' tournament |promotion = [[Consejo Mundial de Lucha Libre]] |date=May 15, 2015 to May 22, 2015 |attendance= |venue=[[Arena Mexico]] |city = [[Mexico City, Mexico]] |liveevent=Y |lastevent=''[[CMLL Reyes del Aire#CMLL Reyes del Aire 2015|Reyes del Aire]]'' (2015) |nextevent=''[[En Busca de un Ídolo 2015|En Busca de un Ídolo]]'' 2015 |event=''Leyenda de Plata'' |lastevent2=''[[Leyenda de Plata#Leyenda de Plata 2014|Leyenda de Plata]]'' (2014) |nextevent2=TBA }} On May 8, 2015 [[Consejo Mundial de Lucha Libre]] (CMLL) announced that the '''2015 ''Leyenda de Plata''''' tournament would begin the following Friday, May 15, as part of the Friday Night ''[[CMLL Super Viernes|Super Viernes]]'' show. The participants of the first round were: [[Bárbaro Cavernario]], [[Dragon Lee II|Dragon Lee]], [[Fuego (wrestler)|Fuego]], [[Hiromu Takahashi|Kamaitachi]], [[Luciferno]], [[Mephisto (wrestler)|Mephisto]], [[Místico II|Místico]], [[Niebla Roja]], [[The Panther (wrestler)|The Panther]], [[Titán (wrestler)|Titán]], [[Virus (wrestler)|Virus]] and [[Volador Jr.]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cmll.com/01_cartelera/c_arena_mexico.htm |title=Viernes 15 de Mayo '15 |publisher=[[Consejo Mundial de Lucha Libre]] |language=Spanish |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141104124841/http://cmll.com/01_cartelera/c_arena_mexico.htm |archivedate=2014-11-04 |df= }}</ref> In the end Dragon Lee pinned Virus to win the ''torneo cibernetico'', which meant he would face the previous year's winner [[Negro Casas]] the following week.<ref name=YahooLdP2015>{{cite web | url=https://es-us.deportes.yahoo.com/fotos/lucha-libre-función-viernes-15-de-mayo-slideshow/;_ylt=Ao_NIat8CpmrSNzUP_NUY9727tx_;_ylu=X3oDMTE2ZGx1dWc1BG1pdAMEcG9zAzMEc2VjA01lZGlhQkNhcm91c2VsTWl4ZWRMUENB;_ylg=X3oDMTBhNjZjMG5uBGxhbmcDZXMtVVM-