==Leyenda de Plata 2016== {{Infobox wrestling event |name=''Leyenda de Plata'' (2016) |image=Leyenda de Plata 2016.jpg |caption=Official poster for the event, listing [[Negro Casas]] as a participant. |promotion = [[Consejo Mundial de Lucha Libre]] |date=July 15, 2016 - July 22, 2016 |attendance= |venue=[[Arena Mexico]] |city = [[Mexico City, Mexico]] |liveevent=Y |lastevent=''[[CMLL International Gran Prix (2016)|CMLL International Gran Prix]]'' (2016) |nextevent=[[CMLL 83rd Anniversary Show]] |event=''Leyenda de Plata'' |lastevent2=''[[Leyenda de Plata#Leyenda de Plata 2015|Leyenda de Plata]]'' (2015) |nextevent2=TBA }} The '''2016 ''Leyenda de Plata''''' (Spanish for "Silver Legend") was anannual [[professional wrestling]] tournament held by the Mexican [[Consejo Mundial de Lucha Libre]] ("World Wrestling Council" in English; CMLL) that is slated to start on July 15, 2016. The ''Leyenda de Plata'' tournament honors ''[[lucha libre]]'' legend [[El Santo]] and has been held on an almost-annual schedule since 1998. The tournament consists of a ''[[torneo cibernetico]]'' elimination match as the first round and the winner of that match would face the previous' year's winner in the finals. For the 2016 tournament CMLL originally announced that the [[#Leyenda de Plata 2015|2015 tournament winner]], [[Negro Casas]], was part of the initial field, but later replaced him with [[Dragon Lee II|Dragon Lee]] to keep the original format intact.
The ''torneo cibernetic'' competitors included: [[Bárbaro Cavernario]], Dragon Lee, [[Guerrero Maya Jr.]], [[La Máscara (wrestler)|La Máscara]], [[Mephisto (wrestler)|Mephisto]], [[Místico II|Místico]], [[The Panther (wrestler)|the Panther]], [[Psicosis II|Ripper]], [[Titán (wrestler)|Titán]], [[Tritón (wrestler)|Tritón]], [[Virus (wrestler)|Virus]] and [[Volador Jr.]]<ref name=YahooLdP2016/> During the final moments of the ''torneo cibernetico'' La Máscara applied the ''[[Boston crab#Reverse Boston crab|La Campana]]'' submission hold on Dragon Lee, when Lee's older brother [[Rush (wrestler)|Rush]] ran to the ring and attacked La Máscara to cause a disqualification. After the match, Dragon Lee challenged La Máscara to a ''[[Lucha de Apuestas]]'' match, but La Máscara did not accept the match at the time. After the challenge, La Máscara attacked Dragon Lee and stole Dragon Lee's mask.<ref name=YahooLdP2016>{{cite web | url=https://es-us.deportes.yahoo.com/fotos/lucha-libre-arena-m%C3%A9xico-torneo-leyenda-de-plata-2016-slideshow/ | title=Lucha Libre Arena México, Torneo Leyenda de Plata 2016 | date=July 16, 2016 | accessdate=July 17, 2016 | publisher=[[Yahoo!]] | work=Yahoo Deportes! | first=Gonzalo | last= López Peralto| language= Spanish}}</ref><ref name=MedioLdP2016>{{cite web | url=http://www.mediotiempo.com/lucha-libre/2016/07/16/la-mascara-con-plateado-opaco | title=La Máscara con 'plateado opaco' | date= July 16, 2016 | accessdate=July 17, 2016 | work=MedioTiempo | publisher=[[MSN]] | language= Spanish | first=Apolo | last=Valdés}}</ref><ref name=SLLdP2016>{{cite web | url=http://superluchas.com/2016/07/16/cmll-resultados-viernes-espectacular-de-arena-mexico-15072016-la-mascara-finalista-del-torneo-la-leyenda-de-plata/ | title=CMLL: Resultados Viernes Espectacular de Arena México – 15/07/2016 – La Máscara, finalista del Torneo “La Leyenda de Plata” | date=July 16, 2016 | accessdate=July 17, 2016 | work=Super Luchas Magazine | language=Spanish}}</ref> The following week La Máscara defeated Negro Casas after interference from Casas' corner man [[Tiger (wrestler)|Tiger]] hit Casas instead.<ref name=LdP2016>{{cite web | url=http://www.mediotiempo.com/lucha-libre/2016/07/23/con-trampa-la-mascara-es-plateada | title=Con trampa, La Máscara es ‘plateada’ | date=July 23, 2016 | accessdate=July 23, 2016 | publisher=[[MSN]] | work=MedioTiempo | language=Spanish | first=Apolo | last=Valdés}}</ref>
