==Leyenda de Plata 2017== {{Infobox wrestling event |name=''Leyenda de Plata'' (2017) |image=Volador Jr. 2016.jpg |caption= [[Volador Jr.]], winner of the tournament |promotion=[[Consejo Mundial de Lucha Libre]] |date=October 13, 2017 to October 20, 2017 |attendance= |venue=[[Arena Mexico]] |city=[[Mexico City]] |liveevent=Y |lastevent=[[CMLL 84th Anniversary Show]] |nextevent=[[CMLL Día de Muertos (2017)]] |event=''Leyenda de Plata'' |lastevent2=[[Leyenda de Plata#Leyenda de Plata 2016|''Leyenda de Plata'' (2016)]] |nextevent2=TBA }} The '''2017''' '''''Leyenda de Plata''''' (Spanish for "Silver Legend") was a [[professional wrestling]] tournament produced by [[Consejo Mundial de Lucha Libre]]. The tournament will be in honor of Mexico's most famous wrestler [[El Santo]]. The tournament is scheduled to be a ''[[torneo cibernetico]]'' elimination match featuring [[Sansón (wrestler)|Sansón]], [[Puma (luchador)|Puma]], [[Mistico II|Mistico]], [[Volador Jr.]], [[Guerrero Maya Jr.]], [[The Panther (wrestler)|The Panther]], [[Carístico]], [[Forastero]], [[Soberano Jr.]], [[Dragon Lee II|Dragon Lee]], [[Negro Casas]], [[Tiger (wrestler)|Tiger]], [[Titán (wrestler)|Titán]], [[Mephisto (wrestler)|Mephisto]], [[Virus (wrestler)|Virus]] and [[Bárbaro Cavernario|Cavernario]] where the last two men in the ring face off in the finals
;Cibernetico (October 13, 2017) <ref>{{cite web | url= http://www.mediotiempo.com/lucha-libre/2017/10/20/volador-jr-consiguio-su-segunda-leyenda-de-plata | title = Volador Jr. consiguió su segunda Leyenda de Plata | date=October 20, 2017 | accessdate=October 22, 2017 | work=Medio Tiempo |language=Spanish}}</ref>
