{{third-party|date=October 2016}} {{Infobox music festival|music_festival_name=Welcome to the Future|image=|location=[[Netherlands]]|years_active=2007 - present|dates=end of July|genre=[[Techno]], [[House music|House]]|website={{URL|welcometothefuture.nl}}}} '''Welcome to the Future''' is a music festival held annually in the [[Netherlands]], near [[Amsterdam]]. It was launched in 2007 in the nature reserve [[Het Twiske]] near [[Amsterdam]]. In 2015, the first indoor day edition was launched in the Warehouse Elementenstraat.
The festival organization anounced that in 2019, the festival will stretch over a full weekend, taking place on Friday, July 19th and Saturday, July 20th with on-site camping grounds.
== Awards == Since 2012 the festival has been rewarded with [[A Greener Festival]] award, and since 2014 with their highest rating.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.agreenerfestival.com/2016/10/first-2016-greener-festival-award-winners-announced-at-ade-green/|title=First 2016 Greener Festival Award Winners Announced at ADE Green|last=|first=|date=|website=|publisher=|access-date=}}</ref> == Line up == {| class="wikitable" ! Year !Date ! Headliners |- |2018 |Saturday, 21 July 2018 |[[Dax J]], Ø [Phase], Honey Dijon, [[Steve Rachmad]], [[2000 And One]], [[Charlotte De Witte]] |- |2017 |Saturday, 22 July 2017 |[[Chris Liebing]], [[Dave Clarke (DJ)|Dave Clarke]], [[Seth Troxler]], [[Loco Dice]], [[Kölsch (artist)|Kölsch]], [[De Sluwe Vos]], [[Kerri Chandler]]<ref>{{cite web|title=Welcome to the Future|url=http://partyflock.nl/party/326720:Welcome-to-the-Future|work=Partyflock|accessdate=2017-05-04|language=nl-NL}}</ref> |- |2016 |Saturday, 23 July 2016 |[[Pan-Pot]], [[Chris Liebing]], [[Len Faki]], [[Paco Osuna]], [[The Martinez Brothers]], [[Andhim]], [[Paul Ritch]] (live) <ref>{{Cite web |url= http://partyflock.nl/en/party/308062:Welcome-to-the-Future-Festival |title= Welcome to the Future 2016 |last=|first= |date= |website= |publisher= |access-date=}}</ref> |- |2015 |Saturday, 25 July 2015 |[[Seth Troxler]], [[Pan-Pot]], [[Len Faki]], [[Chris Liebing]], [[DJ Sneak]], [[Hot Since 82]], [[Gabriel Ananda]] (live), [[Detroit Swindle]] <ref>{{Cite web |url= http://partyflock.nl/party/281713:Welcome-to-The-Future-Festival|title=Welcome to the Future 2015 |last=|first= |date= |website= |publisher= |access-date=}}</ref> |- |2014 |Saturday, 26 July 2014 |[[Loco Dice]], [[Ricardo Villalobos]], [[Chris Liebing]], [[Luke Slater|Planetary Assault Systems]] (live), [[Rødhåd]], [[Groove Armada]], [[Mathew Jonson]] (live), [[Kölsch (artist)|Kölsch]] (live) <ref>{{Cite web|url=http://partyflock.nl/en/party/265963:Welcome-to-the-Future-Festival-2014|title=Welcome to the Future 2014|last=